Meet Listta Pro! Subscribe to complete planning more smoothly: No ads. No limit on the number of projects Extended beeps Key support Listta New Features! Completed tasks and completed events in the project Grouping operations of notes and folders Advanced repeat settings

Each project now has a separate page for easy access to all tasks activities and comments. You can easily focus on a specific direction in your life! Managing tasks and activities just got easier! A catalog of quick and categorized actions can now be accessed from the home screen. Move tasks or activities to other dates assign tasks set reminders and priorities and delete unnecessary items in just a few clicks!

We have launched the following program versions for RTL languages Hebrew version and Arabic version! We ve added the ability to pin important notes to the top of your list! You can now move notes directly from the notes list to the notes folder using the Move option We ve optimized the sound functionality of the apps now they don t pair with music players and don t cause interference when listening to music Added statistics flags with options. You can track the number of open tasks right on your smartphone screen!

We ve added folders to the Notes section! Now that itemization just got a whole lot more convenient! We added sounds for task execution. Now you can choose a unique reminder sound from our favorites! Sound controls are located under Settings.
